###################################################################

Works with UBUNTU

To use the server manager simply type one of these COMMANDS into
 the console and hit ENTER!

These are the current commands listed as "COMMAND - DESCRIPTION"
#Basic commands
manager-start  - Displays Manager  manual
manager-remove - Remove manager from showing at System Start
manager-update - Updates your server repositories

#Install common applications
manager-lamp   - Installs Linux Apache MySQL PHP Stack
manager-pma    - Installs phpMyAdmin (only works if installed lamp b4)
manager-tfs    - LAMP+PMA+TFS+ZNOTE Setup

#TFS
tfs-start      - Starts TFS
tfs-kill       - Force Kills TFS task (NOT RECOMMENDED! Doesnt save!)
